        <div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--ink-muted);">Dr Total: <strong>\u20B91,47,500</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Cr Total: <strong>\u20B91,47,500</strong> &nbsp; <span style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Balanced</span></div>
